        [
          "Michaelangello de Ravenna",
          "Rival for Archbishop: The young Lasombra chile of Judge Inquisitor Bertolli Cinqo. Michael is incredibly devout and his Sire is perhaps the most powerful demon hunter in the Inquistion. In fact, Cinqo served you as a Templar before he joined the inquistion and served you with distinction."
