        [
          "Chalupavka",
          "Rival for Archbishop: A monstrous Tzimsce Elder from Peru.  The mystical elders of her Clan back her completely and the her Priest is an infamoie Black Hand Remover.  She is a great warrior but has few freinds in Mexico City."
        ],
        [
          "Elivira de Cordoba",
          "A Lasombra Elder, she now leads Cardine Scorso - one of the packs that assaulted the haven of the Lasombra Antediluvean.  Her sire was there when you were raised as a Cardinal and when you signed the Code of Milan.  She has many friends amongst the Prisci and Temoch's respoect."
        ],
